          "date": "2012-11-20 08:19:27.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-957 scrub: OI scrub against ldiskfs",
        "message": "LU-957 scrub: OI scrub against ldiskfs\n\nBackport of commit I04d25b3433336fb63c312f795a8631328beb3aa7.\n\nThe OI scrub is totally implemented inside osd-ldiskfs,\nand driven by the inode iterator. For each object with\nnormal fid, its fid in the LMA and related OI entry in\nthe OI file will be compared, if they are inconsistent,\nthen the OI entry will be updated.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <laisiyao@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I5b5ce85c3e0123236f99a09439f0431b5c183482\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
